A curry seedling is created by sowing a curry tree seed in a plant pot filled with soil with a gardening trowel. Once watered, it will grow into a curry sapling. A curry sapling requires level 42 Farming to plant in a fruit tree patch.

Changes[edit | edit source]

Date Changes
10 January 2019
(update)

The watered version was graphically updated to distinguish it from the unwatered version.

30 January 2014
(update)

The watered version was renamed from "Curry seedling" to "Curry seedling (w)".

11 July 2005
(update)
  • The item was made obtainable.
  • The item was renamed from "Plant pot" to "Curry seedling".
  • The item's examine was changed from "Farming skill coming soon!"
6 June 2005
(update)

The item was added to the game cache.
